            "title": "英超｜拉舒福特豪言幫維拉贏歐聯 維拉死線前再連借2人展雄心",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"(左起)阿素迪沙斯、拉舒福特、馬高阿辛斯奧。維拉官方X圖片\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/816d86763a6bed4b12e84bd05a8787a4/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250204/_2025020414080068340.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">(左起)阿素迪沙斯、拉舒福特、馬高阿辛斯奧。維拉官方X圖片</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>曼聯日前將棄將拉舒福特外借至阿士東維拉，此子首以維拉球員身分受訪時就豪言要幫新東家成為歐聯冠軍。而維拉周一在轉會市場死線前就壓哨再連借2人，中場馬高阿辛斯奧和中堅阿素迪沙斯增強實力盡展雄心。\n\n</p><h2>拉舒福特目標助維拉贏歐聯</h2>\n<p>拉舒福特日前落實被曼聯外借到阿士東維拉，將披上9號球衣的他接受維拉官方訪問談到其目標時矢言：「維拉仍有份爭奪歐聯，我希望在歐聯中行得愈遠愈好。如果不以冠軍為目標，就永遠不能成為冠軍。這是我的主要目標，同時在聯賽中繼續努力，盡可能獲得更高排名。」\n\n</p>\n<p>維拉今季在歐聯有不錯的表現，以5勝1和2負排第8直入16強，本身在曼聯也有歐聯經驗的拉舒福特明言:「歐聯是最偉大的賽事，我曾有不少經驗，會與新隊友分享經驗，並利用彼此的經驗來爭勝。我知道當我發揮出最佳狀態時，可以影響勝負。我唯一的目標是協助球隊取勝，並創造歷史。」\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"馬高阿辛斯奧。維拉官方X圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3db23aadea757aa41f1194dc137ef733/2025-02/Gi4rCV9XEAEk2zP.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        馬高阿辛斯奧。維拉官方X圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"拉舒福特。維拉官方X圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6a1f1ac47409f9c1a5c69632af835f86/2025-02/Gi3Zn1VXcAAKwe3.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        拉舒福特。維拉官方X圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"馬高阿辛斯奧。維拉官方X圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/029a3759e5d7c61904045352d66404d9/2025-02/Gi4se7tXcAAQGOq.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        馬高阿辛斯奧。維拉官方X圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"阿素迪沙斯。維拉官方X圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/156e23d155f8faa093c87a631eccaac2/2025-02/Gi56agHWUAAym17.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        阿素迪沙斯。維拉官方X圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"拉舒福特。維拉官方X圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7ee1a67c3dff648cca44dcd8e70bedba/2025-02/Gi0JNFZWkAA6Qo1.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        拉舒福特。維拉官方X圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"阿素迪沙斯。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c7744af88a794035245a6e6e6544e614/2025-02/2024-12-22T143043Z_1535065664_UP1EKCM14B65D_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-ENGLAND-EVE-CHE-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        阿素迪沙斯。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"阿素迪沙斯。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/fbe1260641faa6b24852a96efcfc48fb/2025-02/2024-11-07T202111Z_547851420_UP1EKB71KJ80C_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-CONFERENCE-CHE-NOA-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        阿素迪沙斯。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"拉舒福特。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/41fc2ce698860bc91ccbb02e99d0818c/2025-02/2024-12-30T204142Z_1282652998_UP1EKCU1LHH48_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-ENGLAND-MUN-NEW-REPORT_4_.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        拉舒福特。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"拉舒福特。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2afed650cb0b4b612f6ef6a04d62a4ce/2025-02/2025-02-03T152848Z_906166101_RC2XZBA0XZSS_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-ENGLAND-AVL-RASHFORD.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        拉舒福特。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>連簽2人展示野心</h2>\n<p>而借入拉舒福特後，維拉亦把握機會於周一轉會市場死線日再出手，由巴黎聖日耳門借用中場馬高阿辛斯奧，及借入車路士中堅阿素迪沙斯，明顯準備大展拳腳。曾經隨皇家馬德里3奪歐聯的阿辛斯奧也直言：「我熟悉歐聯比賽，勝負是由小細節決定，我們會做好準備。」\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
